{"tid":1718143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家勿忘初衷！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T19:18:20.000Z","uid":35726,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"462dceae6448a38e6285ef0e2a3e4e4a7c39877d","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"要記得我哋由星期一開始做三罷行動既目的！<br />\n本來就喺一場消耗戰<br />\n要令到社會停止運作 迫政府就範！！<br />\n而唔係同班黑警開戰呀！！<br />\n明白大家而家戰意好高<br />\n但同狗對抗 從來都唔係目標<br />\n只會令更多手足受傷<br />\n我哋係 迫 不 得 意 先開戰 而唔喺主動執搵佢地挑機！<br />\n要對準個垃圾政府同政權<br />\n有時間 不如諗下仲有無咩其他方法 可以令三罷行動更加成功<br />\n例如點繼續喺一啲主要路段上塞<br />\n大欖？東隧？ 呢啲地方都未試過<br />\n大家可以各施其職<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n要記得 黑警係要清算 但要對準政權 先可以成功令黑警永無反生之日<br />\n仲有好耐無講過啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 不放棄<br />\n香港人 戰鬥！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed429305f9c005a66cfcbe97fc1b0c2a73f3e2a7","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"6f923494d98edd59ea19a09eff88a9d60bbb3a12","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772d04330f92e6447043c77b4768de2721d1d541","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:53:57.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39bb257bfd7e1847b38b15b0612a3f5fd7c0f53","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcf92746062c10bd81872459b45076379bf5f54","tid":1718143,"uid":35726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:55:22.00